50367d821d5dce5bd952a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F18%2F130611_5a5650fc99350367d821d5dce5bd952a.jpg&h=9fe6a7dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/18/130611_4a39f28fa88afe2a0292a16a41f804ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F18%2F130611_4a39f28fa88afe2a0292a16a41f804ad.jpg&h=aecf600b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n狗先食大快活</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/18/131527_ec89e7438e4bc61d5d79680af41a1086.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F18%2F131527_ec89e7438e4bc61d5d79680af41a1086.jpg&h=197c1323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食咁多味精，身體唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891ebb53cb0ff666fa0719f4cbf226f62edd8b54","tid":501944,"uid":147737,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:18:48.000Z","msg":"香港人就係咁，以為人哋做咩都有利益收<br />\n完全想像唔到人係可以因為真心欣賞而表揚下人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cca9a3ab123d1aa95262df1a67d17e804ede4a4","tid":501944,"uid":69191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:26:24.000Z","msg":"尋日朝早落大快活食早餐<br />\n收銀係串少少但都係對一啲on9客<br />\n水吧就好和諧<br />\n雖然忙到出汁，佢地都有講有笑咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個執餐姨姨仲好有禮貌、有笑容"},{"pid":"fe3fd21978b1e12260b369718aa2b0d655d7ec58","tid":501944,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:30:23.000Z","msg":"收銀同水吧d呀姐成日都好唔妥咁串黎串去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a39ec2d35d511ce039e86e1774ec3765e095ca2d","tid":501944,"uid":19141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:31:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過大快活打邊爐 啲呀姐真係好好招呼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n招佢老母呼<br />\n講起就把撚火<br />\n有次打邊爐叫一豬一牛<br />\n叫完坐底等<br />\n送到黎果陣黎左兩個豬<br />\n之後一聲唔出走撚左<br />\n我叫返佢轉頭話叫左一豬一牛<br />\n佢話無牛<br />\n咁我問佢兩者係咪有差價<br />\n佢答我咁真係無牛呀嘛<br />\n屌老母個情況真係好似'任嗌架喎'咁<br />\n之後我死死氣去收銀講<br />\n條收銀員又叫主任黎<br />\n搞撚左成十分鐘先拎得返果幾蚊<br />\n講起就把撚火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後永世ban大快活"},{"pid":"3065340032912b7b0acc26996a3872c511a5c573","tid":501944,"uid":100633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T05:53:07.000Z","msg":"一撚樣"},{"pid":"9c44b242a4010d8936ee13dae149b8feb5b1b939","tid":501944,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T09:42:02.000Z","msg":"因為有曹美女"},{"pid":"4d51b0c36d4b6f5cc591027e8757035fe6d0d6ca","tid":501944,"uid":20449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:17:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5b5f51f160668dbb3918edccba487002cee343c","tid":501944,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T11:29:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我樓下個間有弱能㗎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n弱能都可以好服務</blockquote><br />\n其實肯請弱能唔係證明間工司好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肯承擔社會責任<br />\n對員工衰極都有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nM記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請啲弱能返黎倒鳩我可樂<br />\n鬧佢就歧視都唔知鬧唔鬧好"},{"pid":"2e01b033469391feda6496bd9a52cd3e81a1ca97","tid":501944,"uid":69484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T12:12:21.000Z","msg":"邊有咁多打手 <br />\n純粹見到大快活好過大家樂 <br />\n想屌下姐"},{"pid":"41c1a79bfa558b42e8c47de2a9c182d62b8d46d1","tid":501944,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T12:36:36.000Z","msg":"上次膽粗粗試完個新出個吉列豬真係返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺尖沙咀嗰間食<br />\n<br />\n好食過好多偽日本餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n重要有人專乘送飯嚟 真係窩心<br />\n<br />\n利申非打手"},{"pid":"2465543e193a016c590f07759e730495e6dbec80","tid":501944,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T12:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊有咁多打手 <br />\n純粹見到大快活好過大家樂 <br />\n想屌下姐</blockquote><br />\n有啲嘢真係事實<br />\n大家樂啲打手好心唔好話人打手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好肉酸啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23dbe472b32227b5f2b6f1b3d48b99171aae3e3","tid":501944,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T12:49:02.000Z","msg":"大家樂紅底啦<br />\n<br />\n看下公司架構啦"},{"pid":"bb0b297e777d3650fd9243e1d8d09f46b6e39473","tid":501944,"uid":6009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-18T12:50:46.000Z","msg":"最憎大家樂個D阿姐 無啦啦先生你好 小姐你好<br />\n好撚做作 班管理層唔係咁就以為對客好 有禮貌啊 唔講仲好"},{"pid":"b868d99dc14cf8813a1744cde75ff706bf1f9f4e","tid":501944,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:01:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人就係咁，以為人哋會以為做咩都有利益收先叫打手，以為利益得錢<br />\n完全想像唔到人係可以因為真心欣賞都可以成為打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5baf80a30271b6cd900b8ebeef1d58c12277b781","tid":501944,"uid":103145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:25:27.000Z","msg":"講起就把鬼火！<br />\n本身好日唔食一次，嗰日喺大家樂買2個打邊爐加2杯特飲。<br />\n咁買完就咁俾張有number飛我，埋位等叫number啦，等好撚耐都冇，就去問佢。屌佢老母，原來要交咗飛先等number<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，態度仲要好串。<br />\n好喇，等到有得拎啦，少咗2杯特飲，我仲好好態度咁問佢2杯特飲呢？佢竟然問我拎飛，咁之前我交飛咪俾咗佢囉，仲串串貢話冇飛冇得飲。<br />\n我真係即刻火都黎埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即場拎我張收據俾佢睇，都係態度勁差咁話，唔睇呢張單，最後淪落到即場大聲屌佢幾個老母，用粗口理論咗一輪，最後有一個好似高級少少既呀嬸話，好啦好啦俾佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，嘩，真係多撚謝你，全靠你我先有得飲。<br />\n搞到好似施捨我咁，從此冇再去過。<br />\n<br />\n垃圾大家樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1999"},{"pid":"0531ba7718cb4392319449677a32130326d416ac","tid":501944,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946b622147db0d73a46b1aa5d5b9af2fb7b17837","tid":501944,"uid":43507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:31:43.000Z","msg":"以前做過大家樂收銀pt<br />\n好harsh 病到嘔埋都照收錢唔俾走<br />\n請假都唔俾，至於野食又唔覺好大分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b646084354821f24685e623b84b1540166444fb","tid":501944,"uid":23088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T07:38:02.000Z","msg":"食襯大家樂都會中伏<br />\n<br />\n上次整左個粥底燒鴨瀨粉俾我<br />\n<br />\n見到都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a367c272f22a065d7739b8473d26c70b68f130","tid":501944,"uid":94402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T09:23:11.000Z","msg":"講到員工質素<br />\n<br />\n我屋企附近就大家樂大快活都有<br />\n基本上除左某一間大快活啲丫嬸西到無人有之外(啲人寧願行遠少少去另一間大快活)<br />\n其實睇唔出大家樂同大快活啲員工分別有樓上講到咁大<br />\n<br />\n至於講味道,大快活又真係好食啲嘅"}]}